Lenovo B40-45 (59-436667) Laptop (AMD APU E1- 4GB RAM- 500GB HDD- 14 Inches- DOS- 2GB Graphics) (Black)

Powered with AMD APU E1, Lenovo B40-45 (59-436667) Notebook is the perfect blend of style and excellent performance. Featuring 4GB DDR3 RAM, the laptop delivers outstanding performance no matter what kind of task you throw at it. Catering to your everyday computing needs, the notebook is simply the rightmost choice for students as well as professionals. Featuring 500 GB hard disk capacity, this notebook offers plenty of storage space to the users. You can store almost all kinds of media in this Lenovo B40-45 (59-436667) Notebook. Further, the laptop is provided with 14 inches screen with a screen resolution of 1366 x 768 pixels that offers an amazing visual clarity. Further, it comes packed with connectivity features like USB ports, Bluetooth, etc. Available in classy grey shade, the Lenovo B40-45 (59-436667) Notebook is definitely a must-buy product.
